casebody.data:
Billie Jolee GRAY, Appellant,
v.
STATE of Missouri, Respondent. WD 81443 Missouri Court of Appeals, Western District. ORDER FILED: March 5, 2019 Susan Hogan, Kansas City, MO, Counsel for Appellant. Justin Moody, Jefferson City, MO, Counsel for Respondent. Before Division One: Cynthia L. Martin, P.J., Victor C. Howard, and Thomas H. Newton, JJ.

ORDER

Per Curiam:

Ms. Billie Jolee Gray appeals the Livingston County Circuit Court judgment denying her amended Rule 24.035 motion following an evidentiary hearing. We affirm. Rule 84.16(b).
